    "Similarly, P8 said: \"What I find really hard in this kind of discussion is that it is hidden for you as well, right?",
    "You pay a certain price to Google and OpenAI, which use a lot of energy to create these AI models.",
    "And for their client to provide insights into our AI footprint, these big tech companies should make this more visible.",
    "Right now, you do not really see them, and you cannot make it really tangible how much CO 2 a specific question just generated.\"",
    "Lastly, Founder P2 concluded: \"So, because we are not hosting our own hardware, I do not feel in control of actually doing anything with this."
  ],
